Package: langevinSSM
Type: Package
Title: Habitat-Driven Langevin Diffusion with Spatial Uncertainty
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2026-03-30
Authors@R: person(given = "Brett",
                  family = "McClintock",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "brett.mcclintock@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Brett McClintock <brett.mcclintock@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for simulating and fitting habitat-driven Langevin diffusion models to animal telemetry data subject to location measurement error, missing data, and temporal irregularity (i.e. continous time).
